&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; *Summary*
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Add a language feature to WGSL, `texture_and_sampler_let` that adds the
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; ability to store texture and sampler objects into a let declaration in
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; WGSL.
