&gt;&gt; On Mon, 19 Jan 2026 at 23:49, Daniel Herr &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="c2a6a3acaba7aeaaa7b0b0b1ada4b6b5ececec82a5afa3abaeeca1adaf"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
