&lt;pre&gt;On Tue, Nov 11, 2025 at 5:34 PM Camille Lamy &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="c8aba4e6e6e688afa7a7afa4ade6aba7a5"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

