&lt;tt&gt;One concern I have is once we remove the `top-level-storage-access` &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;permission, `navigator.permissions.query` will throw a TypeError. Of the &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;~1% of pages using rSAFor, do we know how many of them are using &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;tt&gt;`navigator.permissions.query`? &lt;/tt&gt;&lt;pre style="margin: 0em;"&gt;
