&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20251224" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 24 Dec 2025 15:38:29 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
