says

   1. 

   Let parsed be the result of parsing 
   &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-syntax/#parse-grammar"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-syntax/#parse-grammar&lt;/a&gt;&gt; the given value as 
   a CSS &lt;length&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values/#lengths"&gt;https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values/#lengths&lt;/a&gt;&gt;.

