&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="d3b2b7fdfdfd93b0a1fea0a7b2a7a6a0fdb2a3a3a0a3bca7beb2babffdb0bcbe"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
