&gt;&gt;&gt; On Mon, 19 Jan 2026 at 23:49, Daniel Herr &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e98d8887808c85818c9b9b9a868f9d9ec7c7c7a98e84888085c78a8684"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; 
